INSERT INTO
            l1_batches (
                number,
                timestamp,
                protocol_version,
                fee_address,
                l1_gas_price,
                l2_fair_gas_price,
                fair_pubdata_price,
                pubdata_limit,
                l1_tx_count,
                l2_tx_count,
                bloom,
                priority_ops_onchain_data,
                initial_bootloader_heap_content,
                used_contract_hashes,
                created_at,
                updated_at,
                is_sealed,
                settlement_layer_type,
                settlement_layer_chain_id
            )
            VALUES
            (
                $1,
                $2,
                $3,
                $4,
                $5,
                $6,
                $7,
                $8,
                0,
                0,
                ''::bytea,
                '{}'::bytea [],
                '{}'::jsonb,
                '{}'::jsonb,
                NOW(),
                NOW(),
                FALSE,
                $9,
                $10
            )
